                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1390-18450616 t18450616-1390-punishment-124"></join>Confined One Month</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Edward Bullock, Esq.</hi>
